Package services

Class SerialDataService

Object
SerialDataService
All Implemented Interfaces:
IFileDataService
public class SerialDataService extends Object implements IFileDataService
Handles serialization and deserialization of different data types to and from disk. This class supports operations for orders, users, branch users, menu items, payment methods, branches, and password data.
